hadiths[112]{hadithnumber,text}:
2158,"abu-Umama bin Sehal bin Hanif Raziallahu anhuma jab baaghiyon ney Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) key ghar ka muhaasra kar rakha tha to unhoney apney ghar ki chhat par aa kar kaha : main tumhen Allah Taala ki qism deta hun, kya tum nahin jantey ho ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' teen Suraton key siwa kisi musalman ka khoon halal nahin : shaadi key baad zina karna , ya Islam laney key baad murtad ho jana , ya kisi ko nahaq qatl karna jiskey badley mein qatil ko qatl kya jaey, Allah ki qism ! mainey na jahiliyat mein zina kya hai na Islam mein , na Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey baiat karney key baad main murtad huwa hun aur na hi Allah key haram karda kisi nafs ka qatil hun, phir ( aakhir ( tum log kis wajeh sey mujhey qatl kar rahey ho? Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- isey Hammad bin Salma ney Yahya bin Saeed key wastey sey marfooan riwayat kya hai, aur Yahya bin Saeed Qataan aur doosrey kaee logon ney Yahya bin Saeed sey ye hadees riwayat ki hai, lekin ye maqoof hai na ke marfoo, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Masood , Aaisha aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 4- aur ye hadees Usman key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey kaee deegar sanadon bhi sey marfooan marvi hai."
2159,"mainey hajjatul-wadaa mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko logon sey khitab kartey suna : '' ye kon sa din hai? '' logon ney kaha : Haje-Akbar ka din hai padhi. , aap ney farmaya : '' tumharey khoon , tumharey maal aur tumhari izzat o aabroo tumharey darmiyan isi tarah haram hain jaisey tumharey is shehar main tumharey is din ki hurmat o taqaddus hai, khabrdar! jurm karney waley ka wabal khud usi par hai, khabrdar! baap key qusur ka muaakhza betey sey aur betey key qusur ka muaakhza baap sey na hoga, sun lo! shetan hamesha key liye is baat sey mayus ho chuka hai ke tumharey is shehar mein iski puja hogi , albatta un chizon mein uski kuch itaat hogi jinko tum haqeer amal samajhtey ho, wo usi sey khush rahega ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- zyada ney bhi shabeeb bin gharqada sey usi jaisi hadees riwayat ki hai, hum is hadees ko sirf shabeeb bin gharqada ki riwayat sey jantey hain, padhi. 3- is bab mein abu-Bakra, ibne-Abbas, Jabir, Hazim bin Amr Saadi (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2160,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tum mein sey koi shakhs khel kood mein ho ya sanjeedagi mein apney bhai ki lathi na ley aur jo apney bhai ki lathi ley, to wo usey wapis kar dey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf ibne-Abi Zi-ib hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain, 2- Saaib bin Yazeed ko sharfe-sohbat hasil hai bachpan mein unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey kaee hadisein suni hain, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki wafat key waqt unki umr saat saal thi, unkey walid Yazeed bin Saaib padhi. ki bahut sari hadisein hain, wo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key as-haab mein sey hain, aur Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey hadisein riwayat ki hain, Saaib bin Yazeed namr key behan key betey hain, padhi. 3- is bab mein ibne-Umar, Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Sarad, Jaada , aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2161,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath (merey walid) Yazeed (Raziallahu anhu) ney hajjatul-wadaa kya, us waqt mein saat saal ka tha. Yahya bin Saeed Qataan kehtey hain : Muhammad bin Yusuf sabt aur sahab hadees hain, Saaib bin Yazeed unkey nana they, Muhammad bin Yusuf kehtey they : mujh sey Saaib bin Yazeed ney hadees bayan ki hai, aur wo merey nana hain."
2162,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo shakhs apney bhai ki taraf hathiyar sey ishara karey to farishtey is par lanat bhejtey hain ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai, 2- ye Khalid Haza ki riwayat sey gharib samjhi jati hai, 3- Ayub ney Muhammad bin Sirin key wastey sey Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey usi jaisi hadees riwayat ki hai, lekin usey marfooan nahin bayan kya hai aur is mein ye izafa kya hai (وإن كان أخاه لأبيه وأمه)'' agar-che uska saga bhai hi kyon na ho'' , 4- is bab mein abu-Bakra , ummul-momenin Aaisha aur Jabir (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2163,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney nangi talwaar leney aur deney sey mana farmaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hammad bin Salma ki riwayat sey Hasan gharib hai, 2- ibne-Lahia ney ye hadees (عن أبي الزبير an جابر an بنة الجهني an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم)  ki sanad sey riwayat ki hai, 3- merey nazdik Hammad bin Salma ki riwayat ziyada sahih hai, 4- is bab mein abu-Bakra sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2164,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney Fajr padh li wo Allah ki panah mein hai, phir (is baat ka khayal rakho ke) Allah Taala tumharey dar-pai na ho jaey uski panah todney ki wajeh sey '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Jundub aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2165,"maqam jaabiya mein) merey walid ( umr (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey darmiyan khutba deney key liye khadey huye, unhoney kaha : logo ! main tumharey darmiyan isi tarah ( khutba deney key liye ( khada huwa hun jaisey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam hamarey darmiyan khadey hotey they, aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main tumhen apney Sahaba ki perwi ki wasiyat karta hun, phir unkey baad aaney walon (yani Tabe-een) ki phir unkey baad aaney walon ( yani tabaa Tabe-een ( ki, phir jhoot aam ho jaeyga, yahan tak ke qism khilaaey baghair aadmi qism khaye ga aur gawah gawahi talab kiye janey sey pehley hi gawahi dega, khabrdar! jab bhi koi mard kisi aurat key sath khilwat mein hota hai to unkey sath teesra shetan hota hai, tum log jamaat ko lazim pakdo aur parti bandi sey bacho, kyonkey shetan akeley aadmi key sath rehta hai, do key sath uska rehna nisbatan ziyada door ki baat hai, jo shakhs jannat key darmiyani hissey mein jana chahta ho wo jamaat sey lazimi taur par juda rahey aur jisey apni neki sey khushi miley aur gunah sey gham laahiq ho haqiqat mein wohi momin hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai, 2- isey ibne-Mubarak ney bhi Muhammad bin Suqa sey riwayat kya hai, 3- ye hadees kaee sanadon sey umr key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey aai hai."
2166,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah ka haath (uski madad o nusrat) jamaat key sath hota hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum usey ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki riwayat sey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
2167,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Allah Taala meri ummat ko ya ye farmaya : '' Muhammad Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki ummat ko gumrahi par ikhatta nahin kerega, Allah ka haath (uski madad o nusrat) jamaat key sath hai, jo shakhs jamaat sey alag huwa wo jahannam mein gira''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey gharib hai, 2- Suleman (Alaihissalam) Madni merey nazdik Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Sufiyan hi hain, un sey abu-Daawood Tiyalisi, abu-Aamir Aqadi aur kaee ehle-ilm ney riwayat ki hai, padhi. 3- ehle-ilm key nazdik '' jamaat'' sey murad as-haabe-fiq'h aur as-haabe-ilm aur as-haabe-hadees hain, 4- Ali bin Husain kehtey hain ke mainey Abdullah bin Mubarak sey puchha : jamaat sey kon log murad hain? unhoney kaha : abu-Bakar o Umar, un sey kaha gaya : abu-Bakar o umr to wafat paa gaey, unhoney kaha : fulan aur fulan, un sey kaha gaya : fulan aur fulan bhi to wafat paa chukey hain to Abdullah bin Mubarak ney kaha : abu-Hamza Sukri jamaat hain padhi. , 5- abu-Hamza ka naam Muhammad bin Memun hai, wo Saleh aur nek Shekh they, Abdullah bin Mubarak ney ye baat hum sey us waqt kahi thi jab abu-Hamza ba-hayat they."
2168,logo! tum ye aayat padhtey ho يا أيها الذين آمنوا عليكم أنفسكم لا يضركم من ضل إذا اهتديتم '' aey eman walo! apni fikr karo gumrah honey wala tumhen koi zarar nahin pahunchaeyga jab tumney hidayat pa li ''( al-Maeyda : 105) aur mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna hai : ''jab log zalim ko dekh kar uska haath na pakdein (yani zulm na rok den) to qarib hai ke Allah Taala uska azab logon par aam kar dey '' padhi. .
2169,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' us zaat ki qism jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! tum maroof ( bhalai (ka hukm do aur munkir ( burai ( sey roko , warna qarib hai ke Allah Taala tum par apna azab bhej dey phir tum Allah sey dua karo aur tumhari dua qubul na ki jaey '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai."
2170,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! qiyamat us waqt tak qaaim nahin hogi jab tak tum apney Imam ko qatl na kar do , apni talwaaron sey eik doosrey ko qatl na karo aur burey log tumhari duniya key waris na bin jaeyn''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- hum isey sirf Amr bin abi Amr ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
2171,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney us lashkar ka zikr kya jo zamin mein dhansa diya jaeyga, to Umme-Salma ney arz kya : ho sakta hai is mein kuch majbur log bhi hon, aap ney farmaya : '' wo apni niiyaton par uthaey jaeyngey '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai, ye hadees (عن نافع بن جبير an عائشة أيضا an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) ki sanad sey bhi aai hai."
2172,"sab sey pehley ( eid key din ( khutbey ko salaat par muqaddam karney waley Marwan they, eik aadmi ney khadey ho kar Marwan sey kaha : aap ney sunnat ki mukhalifat ki hai, Marwan ney kaha : aey falan ! chhod di gaee wo sunnat jisey tum dhoondtey ho ( ye sun kar) abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha is shakhs ney apna farz pura kar diya, mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna hai : '' jo shakhs koi burai dekhey to chaahiye ke us burai ko apney haath sey badal dey, jisey itni taqat na ho wo apni zaban sey usey badal dey aur jisey uski taqat bhi na ho wo apney dil mein usey bura janey padhi. aur ye eman ka sab sey kamtar darja hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2173,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Allah key hudood par qaaim rehney waley (yani uskey ehkam ki pabandi karney waley) aur uski mukhalifat karney walon ki misal us qom ki tarah hai, jo qura andazi key zariey eik kashti mein sawar hui, baaz logon ko kashti key baalaai (oopri) tabqe mein jagah mili aur baaz logon ko nichley hissey mein , nichley tabqe waley ooper chadh kar pani letey they to baalaai tabqe walon par pani gir jata tha, lihaza baalaai hissey walon ney kaha : hum tumhen ooper nahin chadhney dengey taake hamen takleef pahunchaao (ye sun kar) nichley hissey walon ney kaha : hum kashti key nichey surakh kar key pani leingey, ab agar baalaai tabqe waley unkey haath pakad kar roken gey to tamam najat paa jaeyngey aur agar unhen aisa karney sey mana nahin kerengey to tamam key tamam doob jaeyngey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2174,"Nabi karim Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''zalim badshah key samney haq kehna sab sey behtar jihad hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai. 2- is bab mein abu-Umama sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2175,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik baar kafi lambi namaz padhi , Sahaba ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! aap ney aisi namaz padhi hai ke is sey pehley aisi namaz nahin padhi thi, aap ney farmaya : ''haan , ye ummid aur khof ki namaz thi, mainey is mein Allah Taala sey teen duayen maangi hain, jin mein sey Allah Taala ney do ko qubul kar liya aur eik ko nahin qubul kiya, mainey pehli dua ye maangi ke meri ummat ko aam qehat mein halak na karey, Allah ney meri ye dua qubul kar li, mainey dusri dua ye ki ke in par gheron mein sey kisi dushman ko na musallat kerey. Allah ney meri ye dua bhi qubul kar li , mainey teesri dua ye maangi ke in mein aapas main eik ko doosrey ki ladaai ka maza na chakha to Allah Taala ney meri ye dua qubul nahin farmaee.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Saad aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2176,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah taala ney merey liye zamin samet di to mainey mashriq ( purab (aur maghrib ( pashchim ( ko dekha yaqinan meri ummat ki hukmrani wahan tak pahunch kar raheygi jahan tak merey liye zamin sameti gaee , aur mujhey surkh aur safed do khazaney diye gaey, mainey apney rab sey apni ummat key liye dua ki ke in ko kisi aam qehat sey halak na karey aur na un par gheron mein sey koi aisa dushman musallat kar jo unhen jad sey mita dey , merey rab ney mujh sey farmaya : aey Muhammad ! jab main koi faisla kar leta hun to usey badlta nahin, teri ummat key haq mein teri ye dua mainey qubul ki ke main isey aam qehat sey halak aur barbad nahin karunga , aur na hi in par koi aisa dushman musallat karunga jo in mein sey na ho aur jo inhen jad sey mita dey, bhale hi inke khilaf tamam roey zamin key log jama ho jaeyn, albatta aisa hoga ke inhi mein sey baaz log baaz ko halak kerengey, aur baaz ko qaidi banaeyngey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2177,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney fitney ka zikr kiya aur farmaya : ''wo bahut jald zahir hoga.''  mainey puchha : Allah key Rasool ! us waqt sab sey behtar kon shakhs hoga? aap ney farmaya : ''eik wo aadmi jo apney janweron key darmiyan ho aur unka haq ada karney key sath apney rab ki ibadat karta ho, aur doosra wo aadmi jo apney ghodey ka sar pakdey ho, wo dushman ko darata ho aur dushman usey daratey hon.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai. 2- Les bin Abi Sulem ney bhi ye hadees (عن طاؤس an أم مالك البهزية an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) ki sanad sey riwayat ki hai. 3- is bab mein Umme Mubashshir, Abu Saeed Khudri aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2178,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''eik fitna aisa hoga jo tamam Arab ko apni lapet mein ley lega, iskey maqtool jahannami hongey, us waqt zaban kholna talwaar maarney sey ziyada sakht hoga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko kehtey suna : Ziyad bin Simin Kosh ki uskey ilawa dusri koi hadees nahin malum hai. 3- Hammad bin Salma ney isey Les sey riwayat kartey huye marfooan bayan kiya hai, aur Hammad bin Zaid ney isey Les sey riwayat kartey huye moqufan bayan kiya hai."
2179,"hum sey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney do hadisein bayan kin, jin mein sey eik ki haqiqat to mainey dekh li padhi. , aur dusri ka intizar kar raha hun, aap ney farmaya : ''amanat logon key dilon key jad mein utri phir Qurane-karim utra aur logon ney Quran sey uski ahmiyat Quran sey jaani aur sunnate Rasool sey uski ahmiyat jaani.''  phir aap ney hum sey amanat key uth janey key barey mein bayan kartey huye farmaya : ''aadmi (raat ko) soeyga aur uskey dil sey amanat utha li jaeygi (aur jab wo subah ko utheyga) to uska thoda sa asar eik nuqte ki tarah dil mein reh jaeyga, phir jab dusri baar soeyga to uskey dil sey amanat utha li jaeygi aur uska asar khaal mota honey ki tarah reh jaeyga, jaisey tum apney paaon par chingaari phero to aabla (phaphola) pad jata hai, tum usey phula huwa paatey ho halanke is mein kuch nahin hota'' , phir Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) eik kankari ley kar apney paaon par pherney lagey aur farmaya : ''log is tarah ho jaeyngey ke kharid aur farokht kerengey lekin un mein koi amanat daar na hoga, yahan tak ke kaha jaeyga : falan qabeele main eik amanat-daar aadmi hai, aur kisi aadmi ki tareef mein ye kaha jaeyga : kitna mazbut shakhs hai ! kitna hoshiyar aur aqlmand hai ! halanke uskey dil mein raai key dane barabar bhi eman na hoga.''  Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : merey ooper eik aisa waqt aaya ke kharid aur farokht mein kisi ki parwah nahin karta tha, agar mera fariq musalman hota to uski duniyadari mera haq lota deti aur agar Yahudi ya nasrani hota to uska sardar mera haq lota deta, jahan tak aaj ki baat hai to main tum mein sey sirf falan aur falan sey kharid aur farokht karta hun. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2180,"jab Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Hunain key liye nikley to aap ka guzar mushrekin key eik darkht key paas sey huwa jisey zaat-anwaat kaha jata tha, us darkht par mushrekin apney hathiyar latkaate they, Sahaba ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! hamarey liye bhi eik zaat-anwaat muqarrar farma dijiye jaisa ke mushrekin ka eik zaat-anwaat hai, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Subhan Allah ! ye to wohi baat hai jo Musa (Alaihissalam) ki qom ney kahi thi ke hamarey liye bhi mabood bana dijiye jaisa un mushrikon key liye hai, us zaat ki qism jis key haath mein meri jaan hai! tum guzishta ummaton ki puri puri perwi karogey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- abu Waqid Laisi ka naam Haris bin Auf hai. 3- is bab mein abu Saeed Khudri aur Abu-Hurera Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2181,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''us zaat ki qism jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! us waqt tak qiyamat qaaim nahin hogi jab tak ke darindey insanon sey guftoogu na karney lagen, aadmi sey uskey kodey ka kinara guftoogu karney lagey, uskey jootay ka tasma guftoogu karney lagey aur uski raan us kaam ki khabar deney lagey jo uski biwi ney uski ghair haziri mein anjam diya hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, hum isey sirf Qasim bin Fazal ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 2- Qasim bin Fazal muhaddeseen key nazdik bharosemand aur maamoon hain, Yahya bin Saeed Qataan aur Abdur-Rehman bin Mehdi ney un ki tosiq ki hai. 3- is bab mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2182,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key zamane mein chaand (do tukdon mein) ho gaya to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tum log gawah raho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Masood , Anas aur Juber bin Mut-im (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2183,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hamari taraf apney kamrey sey jhaankaa , us waqt hum qiyamat ka zikr kar rahey they, to aap ney farmaya : ''qiyamat us waqt tak qaaim nahin hogi jab tak tum das nishaniyan na dekh lo ! maghrib (pashchim) sey suraj ka nikalna, Yajuj Majuj ka nikalna, Daabba (janwer) ka nikalna, teen baar zamin ka dhansnaa : eik purab mein , eik pashchim mein aur eik jazeera Arab mein , adn key andar sey aag ka nikalna jo logon ko haankey ya ikhatta kereygi, jahan log raat guzaareingey wahin raat guzaareygi aur jahan log qailula karengey wahin qailula kereygi."
2184,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''log (Allah key) us ghar par hamla karney sey baaz nahin ayengey, yahan tak ke eik aisa lashkar ladaai karney key liye aayega ke jab us lashkar key log maqame beda mein hongey, to unkey aagey waley aur peechchhey waley dhansa diey jaeyngey aur unkey bech waley bhi najat nahin paeyngey (yani tamam log dhansa diye jaeyngey).'' mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! un mein sey jo napasand kartey rahey hon unkey kaamon ko wo bhi? aap ney farmaya : ''Allah taala un ki niyaton key mutabiq unhen uthaeyga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2185,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''is ummat key aakhiri ehad mein ye waqiyat zahir hongey zamin ka dhansnaa, surat tabdeel hona aur aasman sey pathar barasnaa.''  Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) kehti hain ke mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! kya hum halak kar diye jaeyngey halanke hum mein nek log bhi hongey? aap ney farmaya : ''haan , jab fisq (nafarmaani) aur fujoor (buraai) aam ho jaaeygi.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Aaisha ki riwayat sey gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. 2- Raavi Abdullah bin umr Umri key hifz key talluq sey Yahya bin Saeed ney kalam kiya hai."
2186,"suraj doobney key baad mein masjid mein dakhil huwa, us waqt Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam tashrif farma they, aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney puchha : '' Abu-Zar ! jantey ho suraj kahan jata hai? ''main ney arz kya : Allah aur uskey Rasool ziyada jantey hain, aap ney farmaya : '' wo sajdey ki ijazat leney jata hai, usey ijazat mil jati hai lekin eik waqt us sey kaha jaeyga : usi jagah sey niklo jahan sey aaye ho, lihaza wo pashchim sey niklega'' , phir aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney ye aayat padhi : وذلك مستقر لها ''ye uska thikana hai'', Raavi kehtey hain : Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki qirat yehi hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Safwan bin Assal, Huzefa , Usaid , Anas aur abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2187,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam so kar uthey to aap ka chehra Mubarak surkh tha aur aap farma rahey they : « la ilaah illallah» '' Allah key siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin'' aap ney isey teen baar dohraaya, phir farmaya : ''us shar (fitney) sey Arab key liye tabahi hai jo qarib aa gaya hai, aaj Yajuj Majuj ki deewar mein itna surakh ho gaya hai aur aap ney ( haath ki ungliyon sey) das ki gireh lagai '' padhi. , mainey arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! kya hum halak kar diye jaeyngey halanke hum mein nek log bhi hongey ? aap ney farmaya : '' haan , jab burai ziyada ho jaeygi ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- (sanad mein chaar aurton ka tazkira kar key ( Sufiyan bin Uena ney ye hadees achi tarah bayan ki hai, Humedi , Ali bin Madini aur doosrey kaee muhaddeseen ney ye hadees Sufiyan bin Uena sey isi tarah riwayat ki hai, 3- Humedi kehtey hain ke Sufiyan bin Uena ney kaha : mainey is hadees ki sanad mein Zohri sey chaar aurton ka wasta yad kya hai : عن زينب بنت أبي سلمة ، an حبيبة ، an أم حبيبة ، an زينب بنت جحش ‏‏‏‏, padhi. Zenab bint abi Salma aur Habiba Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki soteli ladkiyan hain aur Umme-Habiba aur Zenab bint Jahash Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki azwaje-mutahrat hain, 4- Maamar aur kaee logon ney ye hadees Zohri sey isi tarah riwayat ki hai magar is mein '' Habiba '' key wasta ka zikr nahin kya hai, ibn Uena key baaz shagirdon ney ibn Uena sey ye hadees riwayat kartey waqt is mein '' Umme-Habiba '' key wasta ka zikr nahin kya hai."
2188,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' aakhiri zamana padhi. main eik qom niklegi jis key afrad nau-umr aur satahi aql waley hongey , wo Quran padheingey lekin Quran unkey halaq sey nichey nahin utreyga , Quran ki baat kerengey lekin wo Deen sey isi tarah nikal jaeyngey jaisey shikar sey teer aar paar nikal jata hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- dusri hadees mein Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi hai jis mein aap ney unhen logon ki tarah osaaf bayan kya ke wo log Quran padheingey, magar unkey galey key nichey nahin utreyga, wo Deen sey aisey hi nikal jaeyngey jaisey kamaan sey teer nikal jata hai, un sey maqam Harura ki taraf mansub khawaarij aur doosrey khawaarij murad hain, padhi. 3- is bab mein Ali , abu-Saeed aur Abu-Zar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2189,"eik Ansari ney arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! aap ney falan ko aamil bana diya aur mujhey aamil nahin banaya , Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' tum log merey baad) ghalat ( tarjeeh dekhogey , lihaza tum is par sabr karna yahan tak ke mujh sey hoze- kausar par milo ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2190,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' tum merey baad anqarib ( ghalat ( tarjeeh aur aisey umoor dekhogey jinhen tum bura janogey'', logon ney arz kya : Allah key Rasool! aisey waqt mein aap hamen kya hukm detey hain? aap ney farmaya : ''tum hukkam ka haq ada karna (unki itaat karna) aur Allah sey apna haq maango''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2191,"eik din Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hamen Asr kuch pehley padhaai phir khutba deney khadey huye, aur aap ney qiyamat tak honey wali tamam chizon key barey mein hamen khabar di, yad rakhney walon ney isey yad rakha aur bhoolney waley bhool gaey, aap ney jo baaten bayan farmaain is mein sey eik baat ye bhi thi : ''duniya meethi aur sarsabz hai, Allah Taala tumhen is mein khalifa banaeyga, phir dekhega ke tum kaisa amal kartey ho? khabrdar! duniya sey aur aurton sey bach key raho'', aap ney ye bhi farmaya : '' khabrdar ! haq jaan leney key baad kisi aadmi ko logon ka khof usey bayan karney sey na rok dey '' , abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ney rotey huye kaha : Allah ki qism ! hamney bahut sari cheezen dekhi hain aur) bayan karney sey) dar gaey aap ney ye bhi bayan farmaya : '' khabrdar ! qiyamat key din har ehad todney waley key liye uskey ehad todney key mutabiq eik jhanda hoga aur Imam aam key ehad todney sey badh kar koi ehad todna nahin, us ehad key todney waley ka jhanda uskey peeth key paas nasab kya jaeyga'', us din ki jo baaten hamen yad rahin un mein sey eik ye bhi thi : '' jaan lo ! insan mukhtalif darjey key paida kiye gaey hain kuch log paidaishi momin hotey hain, momin bin kar zindagi guzaartey hain aur eman ki haalat mein duniya sey rukhsat hotey hain, kuch log kafir paida hotey hain, kafir bin kar zindagi guzaartey hain aur kufr ki haalat mein martey hain, kuch log momin paida hotey hain, momin bin kar zindagi guzaartey hain aur kufr ki haalat mein unki maut aati hai, kuch log kafir paida hotey hain, kafir bin kar zinda rehtey hain, aur eman ki haalat mein unki maut aati hai, kuch logon ko ghussa der sey aata hai aur jald thanda ho jata hai, kuch logon ko ghussa jald aata hai aur der sey thanda hota hai, ye dono barabar hain, jaan lo ! kuch log aisey hain jinhen jald ghussa aata hai aur der sey thanda hota hai, jaan lo ! un mein sab sey behtar wo hain jo der sey ghussa hotey hain aur jald thandey ho jatey hain, aur sab sey burey wo hain jo jald ghussa hotey hain aur der sey thandey hotey hain, jaan lo ! kuch log achey dhang sey qarz ada kartey hain aur achey dhang sey qarz wasul kartey hain, kuch log bad-suluki sey qarz ada kartey hain, aur bad-suluki sey wasul kartey hain, jaan lo ! un mein sab sey achcha wo hai jo achey dhang sey qarz ada karta hai aur achey dhang sey wasul karta hai, aur sab sey bura wo hai jo burey dhang sey ada karta hai, aur bad-suluki sey wasul karta hai, jaan lo ! ghussa insan key dil main eik chingari hai kya tum ghussa honey waley ki aakhon ki surkhi aur uski gardan ki ragon ko phooltey huye nahin dekhtey ho? lihaza jis shakhs ko ghussey ka ehsas ho wo zamin sey chipak jaey '' , abu Saeed Khudri kehtey hain : hum log suraj ki taraf mud kar dekhney lagey ke kya abhi doobney mein kuch baqi hai? Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jaan lo ! duniya key guzrey huye hissey ki bih nisbat ab jo hissa baqi hai wo itna hi hai jitna hissa aaj ka tumharey guzrey huye din ki b-nisbat baqi hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Huzaifa, abu-Maryam, abu-Zaid bin Akhtab aur Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, un logon ney bayan kya ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney un sey qiyamat tak honey wali chizon ko bayan farmaya."
2192,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab mulk Sham walon mein kharabi paida ho jaeygi to tum mein koi achai baqi nahin rahegi, meri ummat key eik giroh ko hamesha Allah ki madad sey hasil rahegi, uski madad na karney waley qiyamat tak usey koi nuqsan nahin pahuncha sakengey'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin hawala, ibne-Umar , Zaid bin Sabit aur Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ney kaha ke Ali bin Madini ney kaha : un sey murad ehle-hadees hain."
2193,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' tum merey baad kafir ho kar eik doosrey ki gardanen mat maarna '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Masood , Jareer , ibne-Umar , Kurz bin Alqama , Waasila aur Sunabihi (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2194,"Saad bin abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) ney Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) key daure-khilaafat mein honey waley fitna key waqt kaha : main gawahi deta hun ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' anqarib eik aisa fitna hoga jis mein bethney wala khada honey waley sey behtar hoga, khada honey wala chalney waley sey behtar hoga aur chalney wala dodney waley sey behtar hoga'', mainey arz kya : aap bataiye agar koi merey ghar mein ghus aaye aur qatl karney key liye meri taraf apna haath badhaey to main kya karun? aap ney farmaya : '' Adam key betey (Haabil) ki tarah ho jana ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- baaz logon ney isey Les bin Saad sey riwayat kartey huye sanad mein « رجلا » (eik aadmi (ka izafa kya hai, 3- Saad bin abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey ye hadees dusri sanad sey bhi aai hai, 4- is bab mein abu-Huraira, khabbab bin Arat, abu-Bakra , ibne-Masood , abu Waqid , abu-Musa Ash-ari aur khadsha (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2195,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' tum log nek aamal ki taraf jaldi karo, un fitnon key khof sey jo sakht taareek raat ki tarah hain jis mein aadmi subh key waqt momin aur Sham key waqt kafir hoga, Sham key waqt momin aur subh key waqt kafir hoga, duniyawi saaz o saman key badley aadmi apna Deen bech dega'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2196,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam eik raat bedaar huye aur farmaya : ''subhan Allah! aaj ki raat kitney fitney aur kitney khazaney nazil huye ! hujrey waaliyon (ummahaatul-momeneen) ko koi jaganey wala hai? suno! duniya mein kapda pehanney wali bahut si aurten aakhirat mein nangi hongi''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2197,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''qiyamat sey pehley sakht taareek raat ki tarah fitney ( zahir ( hongey, jin mein aadmi subh ko momin hoga aur Sham mein kafir ho jaeyga, Sham mein momin hoga aur subh ko kafir ho jaeyga, duniyaawi saaz o saman key badley kuch log apna Deen bech dengey''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein abu-Huraira, Jundub, Noman bin Bashir aur abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2198,"is hadees subh ko aadmi momin hoga aur Sham ko kafir ho jaeyga aur Sham ko momin hoga aur subh ko kafir ho jaeyga, ka matlab ye hai ke aadmi subh ko apney bhai ki jaan, izzat aur maal ko haram samjheyga aur Sham ko halal samjheyga."
2199,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey suna, us waqt aap sey eik aadmi sawal kartey huye keh raha tha : aap bataiye agar hamarey ooper aisey hukkaam hukmarani karen jo hamara haq na den aur apney haq ka mutalba keren? Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' unka hukm suno aur un ki itaat karo, isliye ke wo apni zimmedariyon key jawab deh hain aur tum apni zimmedariyon key jawab deh ho '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2200,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' tumharey baad aisey din aaney waley hain jis mein ilm utha liya jaeyga, aur haraj ziyada ho jaeyga '' , Sahaba ney arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! haraj kya chiz hai? aap ney farmaya : '' qatl o khoonrezi''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera , Khalid bin Waleed aur Maaqil bin Yasar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2201,"Nabi karim Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' qatl o khoonrezi key zamaney mein ibadat karna meri taraf hijrat karney key maanind hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees sahih gharib hai, 2- hum isey sirf Hammad bin Zaid ki riwayat sey jantey hain, jisey wo mualla sey riwayat kartey hain."
2202,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab meri ummat mein talwaar chal padeygi to wo qiyamat tak na rukegi'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2203,"merey walid key paas Ali (Raziallahu anhu) aaye aur in ko apney sath ladaai key liye nikalney ko kaha , un sey merey walid ney kaha : merey dost aur aap key chacha zaad bhai ( Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ( ney mujhey wasiyat ki ke '' jab logon mein ikhtilaf ho jaey to main lakdi ki talwaar bana lun '' , lihaza mainey bana li hai, agar aap chahen to usey ley kar aap key sath niklun , Udesa kehti hain : chunanche Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney merey walid ko chhod diya padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf Abdullah bin Ubedullah ki riwayat sey jantey hain, padhi. 2- is bab mein Muhammad bin Muslima (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2204,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney fitney key barey mein farmaya : ''us waqt tum apni kamaanein tod dalo , kamanon ki taant kaat dalo , apney gharon key andar chupkey bethey raho aur Adam key betey (Habil) key maanind ho jao '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib sahih hai."
2205,"main tum logon sey eik aisi hadees bayan kar raha hun jisey mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey suni hai aur merey baad tum sey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey suni hui hadees koi nahin bayan kerega padhi. , unhoney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey suna , aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' qiyamat ki nishaniyon mein sey ye hai : ilm ka uthaya jana , jihalat ka phel jana , zina ka aam ho jana , sharab noshi, aurton ki kasrat aur mardon ki qillat yahan tak ke pachas aurton par eik nigran hoga. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein abu-Musa Ash-ari aur Abu-Hurera Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2206,"hum log Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) key ghar gaey aur un sey hujjaaj key mazaalim ki shikayat ki, to unhoney kaha : ''aaney wala har saal (guzrey huye saal sey) bura hoga, yahan tak ke tum apney rab sey ja milo'', usey mainey tumharey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey suna hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2207,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''qiyamat us waqt tak qaaim nahin hogi jab tak roey zamin par Allah Allah kaha jaeyga'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai.
2208,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' ( qiyamat key qarib ( zamin apney jigar goshey yani khambey ki tarah sona aur chaandi ugleygi, us waqt chor aayega aur kaheyga : isi key liye mera haath kaataa gaya hai, qatil aayega aur kaheyga : isi key liye mainey qatl kya hai, rishta nata todney wala aayega aur kaheyga : isi key liye mainey rishta nata toda tha, phir wo log usey chhod dengey aur is mein sey kuch nahin leingey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
2209,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''qiyamat us waqt tak qaaim nahin hogi jab tak bewaqufon ki aulad duniya mein sab sey ziyada khushnasib na ho jaeyn''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai, hum isey sirf Amr bin abi Amr ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
2210,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab meri ummat pandarah cheezen karney lagey to is par musibat nazil hogi '' , arz kya gaya : Allah key Rasool ! wo kon kon si cheezen hain? aap ney farmaya : ''jab maale-ghanimat ko dolat, amanat ko ghanimat aur zakat ko tawaan samjha jaey, aadmi apni biwi ki farman-bardari karey , aur apni maa ki nafarmani kerega, apney dost par ehsan karey aur apney baap par zulm kerey. masaajid mein aawazen buland honey lagen, razil aadmi qom ka leader bin jaeyga, shar key khof sey aadmi ki izzat ki jaey, sharab pi jaey, resham pahna jaey, (gharon mein) gaaney wali londiyan aur baajey rakhey jaeyn aur is ummat key aakhir mein aaney waley pehley walon par lanat bhejein to us waqt tum surkh aandhi ya zamin dhansney aur surat tabdeel honey ka intizar karo''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai hum isey sirf isi sanad sey Ali bin Abu-Talib ki riwayat sey jantey hain, 2- hum Farj bin Fazala key ilawa doosrey kisi ko nahin jantey jisney ye hadees Yahya bin Saeed Ansari sey riwayat ki ho aur Farj bin Fazala key barey mein kuch muhaddeseen ney kalam kya hai aur unkey hafizey key talluq sey unhen zaeef kaha hai, un sey Wakee aur kaee aimma ney riwayat hadees ki hai."
2211,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab maale-ghanimat ko dolat, amanat ko maale-ghanimat aur zakat ko tawaan samjha jaey, Deen ki taalim kisi doosrey maqsad sey hasil ki jaey, aadmi apni biwi ki farman-bardari kerey. aur apni maa ki nafarmani karey , apney dost ko qarib karey aur apney baap ko door kerega, masaajid mein aawazen buland honey lagen , fasiq o faajir aadmi qabeeley ka sardar bin jaey, ghatiya aur razeel aadmi qom ka leader bin jaeyga, shar key khof sey aadmi ki izzat ki jaeygi, gaaney wali aurten aur baajey aam ho jaeyn , sharab pi jaey aur is ummat key aakhir mein aaney waley apney sey pehley walon par lanat bhejeingey to us waqt tum surkh aandhi , zalzala, zamin dhansney, surat tabdeel honey, pathar barasney aur musalsal zahir honey wali alamaton ka intizar karo, jo us purani ladi ki tarah musalsal nazil hongi jiska dhaaga toot gaya ho''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain, padhi. 2- is bab mein Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2212,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''is ummat mein « khasaf » , padhi. « maskh » aur « qazaf » waqey hoga '' padhi. , eik musalman ney arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! aisa kab hoga ? aap ney farmaya : '' jab naachney waliyan aur baajey aam ho jaeyngey aur sharab khub pi jaeygi ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees « an Aamash an Abdur-Rehman bin saabit an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam » ki sanad sey mursalan marvi hai, 2- ye hadees gharib hai."
2213,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main qiyamat key zamaney hi mein bheja gaya phir main is par sabqat ley gaya jaisey ye ungli is ungli par sabqat ley gaee , aur aap ney apni shahadat aur beech ki ungli ki taraf ishara kya '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees mustaurid bin Shaddad ki riwayat sey gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
2214,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main aur qiyamat is tarah bhejey gaey hain'' ( ye bataaney key liye ( abu-Daawood ney shahadat aur bech ki ungli ki taraf ishara kya, chunanche un dono key darmiyan thoda sa fasla hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2215,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''qiyamat us waqt tak qaaim nahin hogi yahan tak ke tum aisi qom sey lado jis key jootay baal key hongey , aur qiyamat us waqt tak qaaim nahin hogi yahan tak ke tum aisi qom sey lado jis key chehrey teh-b-teh jami hui dhaalon key maanind hongey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein abu-Bakar Siddiq, Barida , abu-Saeed , Amr bin taghlab aur Muawiya (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2216,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab Kisraa halak ho jaeyga to uskey baad koi Kisraa nahin hoga, jab Qaisar halak ho jaeyga to uskey baad koi Qaisar nahin hoga, us zaat ki qism jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! tum unkey khazaney ko Allah key raastey mein kharch karogey (aur ye waqey ho chuka hai) ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2217,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' qiyamat sey pehley Hazare-maut ya Hazare-maut key samandar ki taraf sey eik aag niklegi jo logon ko ikhatta keregi'', Sahaba ney arz kya : Allah key Rasool! us waqt aap hamen kya hukm detey hain, aap ney farmaya : '' tum Sham chaley jana ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki riwayat sey Hasan gharib sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Huzefa bin Usaid , Anas , Abu-Hurera aur Abu-Zar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2218,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''qiyamat us waqt tak qaaim nahin hogi yahan tak ke taqriban tees dajjaal aur kazaab niklengey, un mein sey har eik ye daawa kerega ke wo Allah ka Rasool hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Jabir bin Samra aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2219,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' qiyamat us waqt tak qaaim nahin hogi yahan tak ke meri ummat key kuch qabiley mushrekin sey mil jaeyn , aur buton ki parastish karen, aur meri ummat mein anqarib tees jhootey (dawedar) niklengey , un mein sey har eik ye daawa kerega ke wo Nabi hai, halanke main khaatimunnabiyin hun merey baad koi ( doosra ( Nabi nahin hoga ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2220,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' banu-Saqeef main eik jhoota aur halak karney wala hoga ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : kaha jata hai kazaab aur jhootey sey murad mukhtaar bin abi Ubaid Saqafi aur halak karney waley sey murad Hujjaaj bin Yusuf hai.
2221,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : '' tamam logon sey behtar merey zamaney key log hain, phir unkey baad aaney waley, phirun key baad aaney waley, phir unkey baad aisey log ayengey jo motey taazey hongey, motaapaa pasand kerengey aur gawahi talab karney sey pehley hi gawahi detey phirengey '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Muhammad bin Fuzel ney ye hadees isi tarah (عن الأعمش an علي بن مدرك an هلال بن يساف) ki sanad sey riwayat ki hai, kaee haafizon ney isey (عن الأعمش an هلال بن يساف) ki sanad sey riwayat ki hai, is mein Ali bin mudrik key wasta ka zikr nahin kya hai."
2222,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' meri ummat key sab sey behtar log wo hain jinkey darmiyan mein bheja gaya hun, phir wo log hain jo unkey baad hongey '' , Imran bin Husain kehtey hain : mujhey nahin malum ke aap ney teesrey zamaney ka zikr kya ya nahin, '' phir uskey baad aisey log paida hongey jinsey gawahi nahin talab ki jaeygi phir bhi gawahi detey rahengey, khayanat kerengey amanat daar nahin hongey aur un mein motaapa aam ho jaeyga ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2223,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' merey baad baara ameer ( khalifa ( hongey '' , phir aap ney koi aisi baat kahi jisey mein nahin samajh saka , lihaza mainey apney qarib bethey huye aadmi sey sawal kya to usney kaha ke aap ney farmaya : '' ye baara key baara ( khalifa ( qabila Quraish sey hongey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2224,"mein abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) key sath ibn Aamir key member key nichey tha, aur wo khutba dey rahey they, unkey badan par bareek kapda tha, Abu-Bilal ney kaha : hamarey ameer ko dekho Fasiqon ka libas pehan rakha hai, abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : khamosh raho , mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna hai : '' jo shakhs zamin par Allah key banaey huye sultan ( haakim ( ko zaleel karey to Allah usey zaleel kerega ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
2225,"umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha gaya : kaash! ! aap kisi ko khalifa naamzad kar detey, unhoney kaha : agar main kisi ko khalifa muqarrar karun to abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney khalifa muqarrar kya hai aur agar kisi ko khalifa na muqarrar karun to Rasulullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney khalifa nahin muqarrar kya hai padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees main eik qissa bhi mazkur hai padhi. , 2- ye hadees sahih hai, aur kaee sanadon sey ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey marvi hai."
2226,"hum sey Safina (Raziallahu anhu) ney bayan kya ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' meri ummat mein tees saal tak khilaafat rahegi, phir uskey baad mulukiyat (badshahat) aa jaeygi '' , phir mujh sey Safina (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki khilaafat , umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki khilaafat , Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ki khilaafat aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki khilaafat , shumar karo padhi. , Raavi Hashraj bin Nabata kehtey hain ke hamney isey tees saal paya, Saeed bin Jamhan kehtey hain ke mainey Safina (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : banu Umayya ye samajhtey hain ke khilaafat un mein hai? kaha : banu Zarqa jhoot aur ghalat kehtey hain, balke unka shumar to bad-tareen baadshaahon mein hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- kaee logon ney ye hadees Saeed bin Jamhan sey riwayat ki hai, hum isey sirf Saeed bin Jamhan hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain, padhi. 2- is bab mein umr aur Ali Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney khilaafat key barey mein kisi chiz ki wasiyat nahin farmaai."
2227,"qabila Rabeea key kuch log Amr bin al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) key paas they, qabila Bakr bin Wayl key eik aadmi ney kaha : Quraish baaz rahen padhi. , warna Allah Taala khilaafat ko unkey ilawa jamhur Arab mein kar dega, Amr bin al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : tum jhoot aur ghalat keh rahey ho, mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna hai : '' Quraish qiyamat tak khair ( Islam ( o shar ( jahiliyat ( mein logon key haakim hain'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Masood, ibne-Umar aur Jabir (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2228,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''raat aur din us waqt tak baqi rahengey (yani qiyamat nahin aayegi) yahan tak ke Jahjaah naami eik ghulam badshahat kerega''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai.
2229,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main apni ummat par gumrah kun imaamon (haakimon) sey darta hun '' padhi. , neez farmaya : '' meri ummat ki eik jamaat hamesha haq par ghalib rahegi, un ki madad na karney waley unhen koi nuqsan nahin pahuncha sakengey yahan tak ke Allah ka hukm (qiyamat) aa jaey''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko kehtey suna ke mainey Ali bin Madini ko kehtey suna ke unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki ye hadees '' meri ummat ki eik jamaat hamesha haq par ghalib rahegi'' zikr ki aur kaha : wo ehal hadees hain."
2230,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' duniya us waqt tak khatam nahin hogi jab tak ke merey gharaney ka eik aadmi jo mera hum naam hoga Arab ka badshah na bin jaeyga''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Ali, abu Saeed Khudri, Umme-Salma aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2231,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' merey gharaney ka eik aadmi jo mera hum naam hoga hukumat kerega ''. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : agar duniya ka sirf eik din bhi baqi rahey to Allah Taala us din ko lamba kar dega yahan tak ke wo aadmi hukumat kar ley . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2232,"hum is baat sey darey ke hamarey Nabi key baad kuch haadsaat pesh ayen, lihaza hamney aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey sawal kya to aap ney farmaya : '' meri ummat mein Mehdi hain jo niklengey aur paanch, saat ya no tak zinda rahengey , (us ginti mein Zaidal-amiyi ki taraf sey shak huwa hai'' , Raavi kehtey hain : hamney arz kya : un gintiyon sey kya murad hai? farmaya : saal) aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' phir unkey paas eik aadmi aayega aur kaheyga : Mehdi! mujhey dijiye , mujhey dijiye , aap ney farmaya : '' wo us aadmi key kapdey mein) Dinar o dirham ( itna rakh dengey ke wo utha na sakega ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- abu Saeed Khudri key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey kaee sanadon sey ye hadees marvi hai."
2233,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' us zaat ki qism jis key haath mein meri jaan hai! anqarib tumharey darmiyan Esa bin Maryam haakim aur munsif bin kar utrengey, wo saleeb ko todeingey, Sura ko qatl kerengey, jiziya khatam kar dengey, aur maal ki ziyadti is tarah ho jaeygi ke usey koi qubul karney wala na hoga''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2234,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna : '' Nuh (Alaihissalam) key baad koi Nabi aisa nahin hai jisney apni ummat ko dajjaal sey na daraya ho aur main bhi tumhen us sey dara raha hun '' , phir Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hum sey uska haal bayan kya aur farmaya : '' ho sakta hai mujhey dekhney waley ya meri baat sunney waley kuch log usey paa lein '' , Sahaba ney arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! us din hamarey dil kaisey hongey ? aap ney farmaya : '' aaj ki tarah ya us sey behtar ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees abu-Ubaida bin Jarrah ki riwayat sey Hasan gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Basar , Abdullah bin Haris bin Jizi, Abdullah bin Mughaffal aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2235,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam logon key darmiyan khadey huye aur Allah ki shaan key laaiq uski tareef ki phir dajjaal ka zikr kya aur farmaya : ''main tumhen dajjaal sey dara raha hun aur tamam nabiyon ney us sey apni qom ko daraya hai, Nuh (Alaihissalam) ney bhi apni qom ko us sey daraya hai, lekin main uskey barey main tum sey eik aisi baat keh raha hun jisey kisi Nabi ney apni qom sey nahin kahi , tum log achi tarah jaan logey ke wo kaana hai jabke Allah Taala kaana nahin'', Zohri kehtey hain : hamen umr bin Sabit Ansari ney khabar di ke unhen Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key baaz Sahaba ney bataya : Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jis din logon ko dajjaal key fitney sey dara rahey they (us din) aap ney farmaya : ''tum jantey ho ke koi aadmi apney rab ko marney sey pehley nahin dekh sakta, aur uski aakhon key darmiyan '' ک ,  , ر '' likha hoga, uskey amal ko napasand samajhney waley usey padh leingey'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2236,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Yahud tum sey ladengey aur tum un par ghalib ho jaaogey yahan tak ke pathar kaheyga : aey musalman ! merey peechey ye Yahudi hai isey qatl kar do '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2237,"hum sey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney bayan farmaya : '' dajjaal mashriq ( purab ( main eik jagah sey niklega jisey khurasan kaha jata hai, uskey peechey aisey log hongey jinkey chehrey teh bih teh dhaal ki tarah hongey '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- Abdullah bin Shozab aur kaee logon ney isey abu-Tayyaah sey riwayat kya hai, hum isey sirf abu-Tayyaah ki riwayat sey jantey hain, padhi. 3- is bab mein Abu-Hurera aur Aaisha Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2238,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''badi ladaai, Fateh Qustuntuniya aur khurooje-dajjaal ( ye teeno waqiyat ( saat mahiney key andar hongey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain, padhi. 3- is bab mein Saab bin Jasama, Abdullah bin Basar , Abdullah bin Masood aur abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2239,Qustuntuniya qiyamat key qarib Fateh hoga . Mehmood bin Ghelaan kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai.
2240,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik subh dajjaal ka zikr kya, to aap ney ( uski hiqarat aur uskey fitney ki sangeeni bayan kartey huye dorane-guftgu) aawaz ko buland aur past kya padhi. yahan tak key hamney guman kya ke wo (Madina ki) khajuron key jhund mein hai, phir hum Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas sey wapis aagey, ( jab baad mein) phir aap key paas gaey to aap ney hum par dajjaal key khof ka asar jaan liya aur farmaya : '' kya maamla hai? '' hamney arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! aap ney subh dajjaal ka zikr kartey huye ( uski hiqarat aur sangeeni bayan kartey huye ( apni aawaz ko buland aur past kya yahan tak ke hamen guman honey laga ke wo khajuron key darmiyan hai. aap ney farmaya : '' dajjaal key ilawa dusri chizon sey main tum par ziyada darta hun, agar wo nikley aur main tumharey beech mojud hun to main tumhari jagah khud us sey nimat lunga, aur agar wo nikley aur main tumharey beech mojud na rahun to har aadmi khud apney nafs ka difaa kerega, aur Allah har musalman par mera khalifa (jaa-nashiin) hai, dajjaal ghoongaryaaley baalon wala jawan hoga, uski eik aankh angoor ki tarah ubhri hui hogi to un mein usey abdul-Uzzaa bin Qatan sey tashbih deta hun, pas tum mein sey jo shakhs usey paa ley usey chahiye ke wo Sura Kahaf ki ibtidaai aayaat padhey, wo Sham aur iraaq key darmiyan sey niklega aur daain baaein fasad phelaeyga, Allah key bando! Sabit qadam rehna''. hamney arz kya : Allah key Rasool! rooey zamin par theherney ki uski muddat kya hogi? aap ney farmaya : ''chaalis din, eik din eik saal key barabar hoga, eik din eik mahina key barabar hoga, eik din haftey key barabar hoga aur baqi din tumharey dino ki tarah hongey'', hamney arz kya : Allah key Rasool! bataiye wo eik din jo eik saal key barabar hoga kya us main eik din ki namaz kafi hogi? aap ney farmaya : ''nahin balke uska andaza kar key padhna''. hamney arz kya : Allah key Rasool! zamin mein wo kitni tezi sey apna kaam kerega? aap ney farmaya : ''us barish ki tarah ke jiskey peechey hawa lagi hoti hai (aur wo barish ko nihayat tezi sey purey ilaqey mein phela deti hai), wo kuch logon key paas aayega, unhen dawat dega to wo us ko jhutlayengey aur uski baat radd kar dengey, lihaza wo unkey paas sey chala jaeyga magar uskey peechey peechey un (inkar karney walon) key maal bhi chaley jaeyngey, unka haal ye hoga ke unkey paas kuch bhi nahin rahey, phir wo kuch doosrey logon key paas jaeyga, unhen dawat dega , aur uski dawat qubul kerengey aur uski tasdeeq kerengey, tab wo aasman ko barish barsaney ka hukm dega۔ aasman barish barsaey ga , wo zamin ko ghalla uganey ka hukm dega , zamin ghalla ugaeygi, unkey charney waley janwer Sham ko jab ( charaagaah sey) wapis ayengey, to unkey kohaan pehley sey kahin ziyada lambey hongey, unki kokhein ziyada kushada hongi aur unkey than kamil taur par (doodh sey) bharey hongey , phir wo kisi wiran jagah mein aayega aur us sey kaheyga : apna khazana nikal, phir wahan sey wapis hoga to us zamin key khazaney shehad ki makkhiyon key sardaron ki tarah uskey peechey lag jaeyngey, phir wo eik bharpur aur mukammal jawan ko bulaeyga aur talwaar sey maar kar uskey do tukdey kar dega . phir usey bulaeyga aur wo roshan chehrey key sath hansta huwa aa jaeyga, pas dajjaal usi haalat mein hoga ke usi doran Esa bin Maryam Alaihissalaam dimashq ki mashriqi janib safed meenaar par zard kapdon mein malboos do farishton key bazu par haath rakhey huye utrengey , jab wo apna sar jhukaaeyngey to pani tapkega aur jab uthaeyn gey to us sey moti ki tarah chaandi ki boondein girengi , un ki saans ki bhap jis kafir ko bhi pahunchey gi wo mar jaeyga aur unki saans ki bhap unki hade-nigah tak mehsus ki jaeygi, wo dajjaal ko dhoondeingey yahan tak ke usey baab ludd key paas paa leingey aur usey qatl kar dengey. isi haalat mein Allah Taala jitna chaheyga Esa (Alaihissalam) thehrengey. phir Allah Taala unkey paas wahi bhejeyga ke merey bandon ko taur ki taraf ley jaao , isliye ke mainey kuch aisey bandey utarey hain jin sey lardney ki kisi mein taab nahin hai, '' Allah Taala Yajuj Majuj ko bhejeyga aur wo wesay hi hongey jaisa Allah Taala ney kaha hai : (من كل حدب ينسلون) '' har bulandi sey phel padengey'' ( الأنبياء : ۹۶ ( unka pehla garoh ( Sham ki) buhera tabriya ( naami jhel ( sey guzrega aur uska tamam pani pi jaeyga, phir us sey unka doosra garoh guzreyga to kaheyga : is mein kabhi pani tha hi nahin, phir wo log chaltey rahengey yahan tak ke jabale-baitul-maqdis tak pahuncheingey to kahengey : hamney zamin walon ko qatl kar diya ab aao aasman walon ko qatl keren, chunanche wo log aasman ki taraf apney teer chalaeyngey chunanche Allah Taala unko khoon sey surkh kar key unkey paas wapis kar dega, (us arsey mein) Esa bin Maryam Alaihimussalam aur unkey sathi ghirey rahen gey, yahan tak ke (shadeed qehat saali ki wajeh sey) us waqt bail ki eik siri unkey liye tumharey so Dinar sey behtar malum hogi ( cheezen is qadr mahngi hongi ( , phir Esa bin Maryam aur unkey sathi Allah ki taraf mutawajjeh hongey , to Allah Taala Yajuj o Majuj ki gardanon main eik keeda paida kar dega , jis sey wo sab ekdam eik jaan ki tarah mar jaeyngey, Esa aur unkey sathi ( pahad sey) utrengey to eik baalisht bhi aisi jagah na hogi jo un ki laashon ki gandagi , sakht badboo aur khoon sey bhari hui na ho, phir Esa (Alaihissalam) aur unkey sathi Allah ki taraf mutawajjeh hongey aur Allah Taala aisey badey parindon ko bhejeyga jinki gardanen bakhti oonton ki gardanon ki tarah hongi , wo laashon ko utha kar gaddhon mein phenk dengey, musalman unkey kamaan, teer aur tarkash sey saat saal tak endhan jalaaeingey. phir Allah Taala un par aisi barish barsaeyga jisey koi kachcha aur pakka ghar nahin rok paeyga, ye barish zamin ko dho degi aur usey aainey ki tarah saaf shaffaaf kar deygi, phir zamin sey kaha jaeyga : apna phal nikal aur apni barkat wapis la, chunanche us waqt eik anaar eik jamaat key liye kafi hoga, uskey chilkey sey ye jamaat saya hasil kereygi, aur doodh mein aisi barkat hogi ke logon ki eik badi jamaat key liye eik doodh deney wali oontni kafi hogi, aur doodh deney wali eik gaey logon key eik qabiley ko kafi hogi aur doodh deney wali eik bakri logon mein sey eik gharaney ko kafi hogi, log usi haal mein (kaee salon tak) rahengey ke Allah Taala eik hawa bhejeyga jo sarey mominon ki rooh qabz kar legi aur baqi log gadhon ki tarah khuley aam zina kerengey, phir unhin logon par qiyamat hogi''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, 2- hum isey sirf Abdur-Rehman Yazeed bin Jabir ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
2241,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey dajjaal key barey mein puchha gaya to aap ney farmaya : '' suno ! tumhara rab kaana nahin hai jabke dajjaal kaana hai, uski daahini aankh angoor ki tarah ubhri hui hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Abdullah bin umr ki riwayat sey Hasan sahih gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Saad, Huzaifa, abu-Huraira, Asmaa, Jabir bin Abdullah, abu-Bakra, Aaisha, Anas , ibne-Abbas aur Faltan bin Aasim (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2242,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' dajjaal Madina ( key qarib ( aayega to farishton ko uski nigrani kartey huye paeyga, Allah ney chaha to is mein dajjaal aur taaoon nahin dakhil hoga''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein abu-Huraira, Fatima binte-Qais, Usama bin Zaid, Samra bin Jundub aur Mohjin (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2243,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''emaan Yamen ki taraf sey nikla hai aur kufr mashriq ( purab ( ki taraf sey , sukoon o itminan wali zindagi bakri walon ki hai, aur fakhr o riyaakaari ghodey aur oont walon mein hai, jab Masih dajjaal Uhad key peechey aayega to farishtey uska rukh Sham ki taraf pher dengey aur Sham hi mein wo halak ho jaeyga''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2244,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna : '' ibne-Maryam alaihimussalam dajjaal ko baab ludd key paas qatl kerengey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Imran bin Husain , Nafey bin Utba , abu-Barza , Huzefa bin Usaid , Abu-Hurera , kaisaan , Usman , Jabir , abu-Umama , ibne-Masood , Abdullah bin Amr , Samra bin Jundub, Nawas bin Samaan , Amr bin Auf aur Huzefa bin Yamaan (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2245,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''koi Nabi aisa nahin tha jisney apni ummat ko kaaney aur jhootey (dajjaal) sey na daraya ho, suno! wo kaanaa hai, jabke tumhara rab kaanaa nahin hai, uski dono aakhon key bech '' « ک » , padhi. «  » , padhi. « ر » '' likha huwa hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2246,"Haj ya Umra mein ibne-Saaid ( ibne-Sayyad ( merey sath tha, log aagey chaley gaey aur hum dono peechey reh gaey, jab main uskey sath akeley reh gaya to log uskey barey mein jo kehtey they uski wajeh sey merey raungtey khadey honey lagey aur us sey mujhey khof mehsus honey laga , chunanche jab main sawari sey utra to us sey kaha is darkht key paas apna saman rakh do , phir usney kuch bakriyon ko dekha to piyala liya aur ja kar doodh nikal laya , phir merey paas doodh ley aaya aur mujh sey kaha : abu-Saeed ! piyo , lekin mainey uskey haath ka kuch bhi peena pasand nahin kya, is wajeh sey jo log uskey barey mein kuch kehtey they ( yani dajjaal hai) chunanche mainey us sey kaha : aaj ka din sakht garmi ka hai isliye mein aaj doodh peena behtar nahin samajhta , usney kaha : abu-Saeed ! mainey irada kya hai ke eik rassi sey apney aap ko us darkht sey baandh lun aur gala ghont kar mar jaaun ye is wajeh sey ke log jo merey barey mein kehtey hain, bad-gumaani kartey hain, aap bataiye logon sey meri baaten bhaley hi chupi hun magar aap sey to nahin chupi hain? ansaar ki jamaat ! kya aap log Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki hadees key sab sey badey jaankar nahin hain? kya Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney (dajjaal key barey mein) ye nahin farmaya hai ke wo kafir hai? jabke main musalman hun, kya Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney ye nahin farmaya ke wo baanjh hai? uski aulad nahin hogi, jabke mainey Madina main apni aulad chhodi hai, kya Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney ye nahin farmaya ke wo Madina aur Makka mein dakhil nahin hoga? kya main Madina ka nahin hun? aur ab aap key sath chal kar Makka ja raha hun, abu Saeed Khudri kehtey hain : Allah ki qism ! wo aisi hi daleelen pesh karta raha yahan tak ke main kehney laga : shayad log uskey mutalliq jhoot boltey hain, phir usney kaha : abu-Saeed ! Allah ki qism ! uskey barey mein aap ko sachi baat bataaun ? Allah ki qism ! main dajjaal ko janta hun, uskey baap ko janta hun aur ye bhi janta hun ke wo is waqt zamin key kis khittey mein hai tab mainey kaha : tumharey liye tamam din tabahi ho. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2247,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ibne-Saaid sey Madina key kisi raasta mein miley , aap ney usey pakad liya , wo eik Yahudi ladka tha, uskey sar par eik choti thi, us waqt aap key sath abu-Bakar aur umr Raziallahu anhuma bhi they, aap ney farmaya : '' kya tum gawahi detey ho ke main Allah ka Rasool hun?'', usney kaha : kya aap gawahi detey hain ke main Allah ka Rasool hun? Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main Allah, uskey farishton, uski kitabon, uskey Rasulon aur youme-aakhirat par eman laya hun '' , Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney puchha : '' tum kya dekhtey ho?'' padhi. usney kaha : pani key ooper eik arsh dekhta hun, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tum samandar key ooper iblees ka arsh dekhtey ho'', aap ney farmaya : ''aur bhi kuch dekhtey ho?'' usney kaha : eik sacha aur do jhootey ya do jhootey aur eik sachey ko dekhta hun, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''is par maamla mushtaba ho gaya hai'' , phir aap ney usey chhod diya . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein umr , Husain bin Ali , ibne-Umar , Abu-Zar , ibne-Masood , Jabir aur Hafsa (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2248,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''dajjaal key baap aur maa tees saal tak is haal mein rahengey ke unkey yahan koi ladka paida nahin hoga, phir eik kaanaa ladka paida hoga jis mein nuqsan ziyada aur faeyda kam hoga, uski aankhen soeyngi magar dil nahin soeyga, phir Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney uskey waliden ka huliya bayan kartey huye farmaya : ''uska baap daraz qad aur dublaa hoga aur uski naak chaunch ki tarah hogi, uski maa bhari bharkam aur lambey haath wali hogi'' , abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : hamney Madina key andar Yahud main eik aisey hi ladkey key barey mein suna, chunanche main aur Zuber bin Awam chaley yahan tak ke uskey waliden key paas gaey to wo wesay hi they, jaisa Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney bataya tha, hamney puchha : kya tumhara koi ladka hai? unhoney kaha : hamarey yahan tees saal tak koi ladka paida nahin huwa , phir hum sey eik ladka paida huwa jis mein nuqsan ziyada aur faeyda kam hai, uski aankhen soti hain magar uska dil nahin sota, hum unkey paas sey nikley to wo ladka dhoop main eik moti chadar par letaa tha aur kuch gunguna raha tha, phir usney apney sar sey kapda hataaya aur puchha : tum dono ney kya kaha hai? hamney kaha : hamney jo kaha hai kya tum ney usey sun liya ? usney kaha : haan , meri aankhen soti hain, magar dil nahin sota hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- hum isey sirf Hammad bin Salma ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
2249,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam apney Sahaba ki eik jamaat key sath jismein umr bin Khattab bhi they ibne-Sayyad key paas sey guzrey , us waqt wo bachon key sath bani Maghaala key tilon key paas khel raha tha, wo eik chhota bacha tha isliye usey aap ki aamad ka ehsas us waqt tak na ho saka yahan tak ke aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney apney haath sey uski peeth par maara , phir farmaya : '' kya tum gawahi detey ho ke main Allah ka Rasool hun? '' ibne-Sayyad ney aap ki taraf dekh kar kaha : main gawahi deta hun ke aap ummiyon key Rasool hain, phir ibne-Sayyad ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey kaha : kya aap gawahi detey hain ke main Allah ka Rasool hun? Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main Allah aur uskey Rasulon par eman laya hun '' , phir Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney daryaft kya : '' tumharey paas ( ghaib ki) kon si chiz aati hai? '' ibne-Sayyad ney kaha : merey paas eik sacha aur eik jhoota aata hai, phir Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' tumharey ooper tera maamla mushtaba ho gaya hai'' , phir aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main tumharey liye ( dil mein) eik baat chhipaata hun '' aur aap ney aayat : « يوم تأتي السماء بدخان مبين  chupa li , ibne-Sayyad ney kaha : wo ( chupi hui chiz ( « دخ » hai to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' phitkar ho tujh par, to apni had sey aagey nahin badh sakeyga'', umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Allah key Rasool! mujhey ijazat dijiye main uski gardan uda dun, aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' agar wo haqeeqi dajjaal hai to tum is par ghalib nahin aa saktey aur agar wo nahin hai to usey qatl karney mein koi bhalai nahin hai ''. abdur-Razzaaq kehtey hain : « حقا » sey aap ki murad dajjaal hai padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2250,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''aaj roey zamin par jo bhi zinda hai so saal baad nahin rahega '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar, abu Saeed Khudri aur Barida (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2251,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney apni aakhiri umr main eik raat hamen Isha padhaai , jab aap salam pher chukey to khadey huye aur farmaya : '' kya tum ney apni us raat ko dekha us waqt jitney bhi aadmi is roey zamin par hain so saal guzar janey key baad un mein sey koi bhi baqi nahin rahega ''. ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma kehtey hain : ye sun kar log moghaltey mein pad gaey ke ye to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey aisi hadees bayan kartey hain ke so saal key baad qiyamat aa jaeygi, halanke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney ye farmaya tha ke jo aaj baqi hain un mein sey koi roey zamin par baqi nahin rahega , yani us nasal aur qarn key log khatam ho jaeyngey . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees sahih hai."
2252,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' hawa ko gaali mat do, agar is mein koi naa-pasandida chiz dekho to ye dua padho اللهم إنا نسألك من خير هذه الريح وخير ما فيها وخير ما أمرت به ونعوذ بك من شر هذه الريح وشر ما فيها وشر ما أمرت به''yani aey Allah ! hum tujh sey is hawa ki behtari maangtey hain aur wo behtari jo is mein hai aur wo behtari jiski ye maamoor hai, aur teri panah maangtey hain is huwa ki shar sey aur us shar sey jo is mein hai aur us shar sey jiski ye maamoor hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Aaisha, Abu-Hurera , Usman , Anas , ibne-Abbas aur Jabir (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2253,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam member par chadhey , hansey phir farmaya : '' Tameem daari ney mujh sey eik baat bayan ki hai jis sey mein behad khush hun aur chahta hun ke tum sey bhi bayan karun, unhoney mujh sey bayan kya ke Palestine key kuch log samandar main eik kashti par sawar huye, wo kashti ( toofan mein padney ki wajeh sey) kisi aur taraf chali gaee yahan tak key unhen samandar key kisi jazeera mein dal diya, achcha un logon ney bahut kapdey pehney eik raingney wali chiz ko dekha jis key baal bikhrey huye they, un logon ney puchha : tum kya ho? usney kaha : main jasusi karney wali hun, un logon ney kaha : hamen (apney barey mein) bataao, usney kaha : na main tum logon ko kuch bataaungi aur na hi tum logon sey kuch poochhungi , albatta tum log basti key aakhir mein jaao wahan eik aadmi hai, jo tum ko bataeyga aur tum sey puchega , chunanche hum log basti key aakhir mein aaye to wahan eik aadmi zanjeer mein bandha huwa tha usney kaha : mujhey zaghar ( mulk Sham ki eik basti ka naam hai) key chashmey key barey mein bataao, hamney kaha : bhara huwa hai aur chhalak raha hai, usney kaha : mujhey Besaan ki khajuron key barey mein bataao jo Urdun aur Palestine key darmiyan hai, kya is mein phal aaya ? hamney kaha : haan , usney kaha : mujhey Nabi ( aakhir-uz-zaman Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ( key barey mein bataao kya wo mab-us huye ? hamney kaha : haan , usney kaha : bataao log un ki taraf kaisey jatey hain? hamney kaha : tezi sey , usney zor sey chhalang lagai yahan tak key azad honey key qarib ho gaya, hamney puchha : tum kon ho? usney kaha ke wo dajjaal hai aur tayiba key ilawa tamam shehron mein dakhil hoga, tayiba sey murad Madina hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Shoba key wastey sey Qatada ki riwayat sey Hasan sahih gharib hai, 2- usey kaee logon ney Shaaby key wastey sey Fatima bint Qais sey riwayat kya hai padhi. ."
2254,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' momin key liye munasib nahin hai ke wo apney nafs ko zaleel karey '' , Sahaba ney arz kya : apney nafs ko kaisey zaleel kerega ? aap ney farmaya : '' apney aap ko aisi musibat sey do chaar karey jisey jhelney ki wo taqat na rakhta ho''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
2255,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' apney bhai ki madad karo chahey wo zalim ho ya mazloom'' , Sahaba ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! mainey mazloom honey ki surat main to uski madad ki lekin zalim honey ki surat mein uski madad kaisey karun? aap ney farmaya : '' usey zulm sey baaz rakho , uskey liye yehi tumhari madad hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2256,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney baadiya ( Sehra o biyaabaan ( ki sujoonat ikhtiyar ki wo sakht tabiat wala ho gaya, jisney shikar ka peecha kya wo ghafil ho gaya aur jo badshah key darwazey par aaya wo fitnon ka shikar ho gaya'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki riwayat sey Hasan sahih gharib hai, hum isey sirf Sory ki riwayat sey jantey hain, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2257,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : ( dushmanon par) tumhari madad ki jaeygi, tumhen maal o dolat milegi aur tumharey liye qiley key darwazey kholey jaeyngey, pas tum mein sey jo shakhs aisa waqt paey usey chahiye ke wo Allah sey darey, bhalai ka hukm dey aur burai sey rokey aur jo shakhs mujh par jaan-bujh kar jhoot boley to uska thikana jahannam hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2258,"umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney puchha : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney fitna key barey mein jo farmaya hai usey kis ney yad rakha hai? Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : mainey yad rakha hai, Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ney bayan kya : ''aadmi key liye jo fitna uskey ehal, maal, aulad aur padosi key silsiley mein hoga usey namaz , roza , zakat , amr-bil-maaroof aur nahi anilmunkar mita detey hain'', umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : main tum sey uskey barey mein nahin poochh raha hun, balke us fitney key barey mein poochh raha hun jo samandar ki mojon ki tarah mojen maareyga, unhoney kaha : Ameerul-momenin ! aap key aur us fitney key darmiyan eik band darwaza hai, umr ney puchha : kya wo darwaza khola jaeyga ya tod diya jaeyga? unhoney kaha : tod diya jaeyga, umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : tab to qiyamat tak band nahin hoga. Hammad ki riwayat mein hai ke abu-Waeil Shaqiq bin Salma ney kaha : mainey Masruq sey kaha ke Huzefa sey us darwazey key barey mein poochho unhoney puchha to kaha : wo darwaza umr hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2259,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam hamari taraf nikley aur hum log no aadmi they, paanch aur chaar, un mein sey koi eik ginti waley Arab aur dusri ginti waley ajam they padhi. aap ney farmaya : '' suno : kya tum logon ney suna ? merey baad aisey umra hongey jo unkey paas jaey unki jhooti baaton ki tasdeeq karey aur unkey zulm par unki madad kerey. wo mujh sey nahin hai aur na main us sey hon aur na wo merey hoz par aayega, aur jo shakhs unkey paas na jaey, unkey zulm par un ki madad na karey aur na un ki jhooti baaton ki tasdeeq karey , wo mujh sey hai, aur main us sey hon aur wo merey hoz par aayega''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees sahih gharib hai, 2- hum usey musair ki riwayat sey isi sanad sey jantey hain."
2260,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''logon par eik aisa zamana aayega ke un mein apney Deen par sabr karney wala aadmi aisa hoga jaisey haath mein chingari pakadney wala''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey gharib hai, 2- umr bin Shakir eik Basra Shekh hain, un sey kaee ehle-ilm ney hadees riwayat ki hai."
2261,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab meri ummat akad-akad kar chalney lagey aur baadshaahon ki aulad yani Faras o Rome key baadshaahon ki aulad un ki khidmat karney lagey to us waqt unkey burey log unkey achey logon par musallat kar diye jaeyngey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, abu-Muaawia ney bhi usey Yahya bin Saeed Ansari key wastey sey riwayat kya hai."
2262,"Allah Taala ney mujhey eik chiz sey bacha liya jisey mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey sun rakha tha, jab kisraa halak ho gaya to aap ney puchha : un logon ney kisey khalifa banaya hai? Sahaba ney kaha : uski ladki ko , Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' wo qom hergiz kamiyab nahin ho sakti jisney aurat ko apna haakim banaya'', jab Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ayen yani Basra ki taraf to us waqt mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki ye hadees yad ki, chunanche Allah Taala ney mujhey us sey bacha liya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2263,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam kuch bethey huye logon key paas aa kar thehrey aur farmaya : '' kya main tumharey achey logon ko tumharey burey logon mein sey na bata dun? '' log khamosh rahey , aap ney teen martaba yehi farmaya , eik aadmi ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! kyon nahin? aap hamarey achey logon ko burey logon mein sey bata diijiye, aap ney farmaya : '' tum mein behtar wo hai jis sey khair ki ummid rakhi jaey aur jis key shar sey maamoon ( be-khof ( raha jaey aur tum mein sey bura wo hai jis sey khair ki ummid na rakhi jaey aur jis key shar sey maamoon ( be-khof ( na raha jaey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2264,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' kya main tumhen tumharey achey hukmranon aur burey hukmranon key barey mein na bata dun? achey hukmaraan wo hain jinsey tum mohabbat karogey aur wo tum sey mohabbat kerengey, tum unkey liye duayen karogey aur wo tumharey liye duayen kerengey, tumharey burey hukmaran wo hain jinsey tum nafrat karogey aur wo tum sey nafrat kerengey tum un par lanat bhejogey aur wo tum par lanat bhejengey'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- hum isey sirf Muhammad bin abu-Humed ki riwayat sey jantey hain, aur Muhammad bin abu-Humed hafizey key talluq sey zaeef qarar diye gaey hain."
2265,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''anqareeb tumharey ooper aisey hukmaran hongey jinkey baaz kamon ko tum achcha janogey aur baaz kamon ko bura janogey, pas jo shakhs unkey burey aamal par nakeer karey wo madahnat aur nifaq sey buri raha aur jisney dil sey bura jana to wo mehfooz raha, lekin jo un sey razi ho aur unki ittiba karey ( wo halak ho gaya ( '' , arz kya gaya : Allah key Rasool ! kya hum un sey ladaai na keren? aap ney farmaya : '' nahin, jab tak wo namaz padhtey rahen'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2266,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab tumharey hukmaran , tumharey achey log hon , aur tumharey maaldaar log , tumharey sakhi log hon aur tumharey kaam bahami (aapsi) mashwarey sey hon to zamin ki peeth tumharey liye uskey pet sey behtar hai, aur jab tumharey hukmaran tumharey burey log hon, aur tumharey maaldaar tumharey bakheel log hon aur tumharey kaam aurton key haath mein chaley jaeyn to zamin ka pet tumharey liye uski peeth sey behtar hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- hum isey sirf Saleh al-mari ki riwayat sey jantey hain, aur Saleh al-mari ki hadees mein aisey gharaaib hain jinki riwayat karney mein wo munfarid hain, koi un ki mutaabiat nahin karta, halanke wo b-zaate-khud nek aadmi hain."
2267,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' tum log aisey zamaney mein ho ke jo uska daswaan hissa chhod dey jiska usey karney ka hukm diya gaya hai to wo halak ho jaeyga, phir eik aisa zamana aayega ke tum mein sey jo uskey daswen hissey par amal karey jiska usey karney ka hukm diya gaya hai to wo najat paa jaeyga'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf Nuem bin Hammad ki riwayat sey jantey hain, jisey wo Sufiyan bin Uena sey riwayat kartey hain, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Zar aur abu Saeed Khudri Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2268,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam member par khadey huye aur farmaya : '' fitney ki sar zamin wahan hai aur aap ney mashriq ( purab ( ki taraf ishara kya yani jahan sey shetan ki shaakh ya seeng nikalti hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2269,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' khuraasaan sey kalay jhandey niklengey, un jhandon ko koi chiz pher nahin sakegi yahan tak ke (Palestine key shehar) Eliya mein ye nasab kiye jaeyngey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai."
